entry.title: WEATHER ADVISORY , Killarney
entry.summary: Persons in or near this area should be on the lookout for adverse weather conditions and take necessary safety precautions. Issued: 11:47 AM EST Friday 27 January 2023

entry.title: Friday: Chance of flurries. High minus 1. POP 60%
entry.summary: Cloudy with 60 percent chance of flurries. Wind south 30 km/h gusting to 50 increasing to 50 gusting to 70 early this afternoon. High minus 1. Wind chill near minus 13. UV index 1 or low. Forecast issued 11:30 AM EST Friday 27 January 2023

entry.title: Friday night: Snow. Low minus 7.
entry.summary: Snow and local blowing snow ending overnight then mainly cloudy with 40 percent chance of flurries. Amount 5 to 10 cm. Wind south 40 km/h gusting to 60 becoming west 40 gusting to 60 near midnight. Low minus 7. Wind chill minus 16 overnight. Forecast issued 11:30 AM EST Friday 27 January 2023

entry.title: Saturday: Chance of flurries. Temperature steady near minus 7. POP 40%
